# Completion Review

- Fixed HTTP inventory URL validation to reject missing host.
- Fixed cron validation to reject empty fields instead of collapsing whitespace.
- Fixed latency source selection to return unknown when all latency inputs are missing.
- Fixed heavy-role priority combos to avoid selecting a second primary from same pool.
- Fixed stable allocation ordering to tolerate missing current scores.
- Fixed scanner false-removal guard to require newest successful omission older than five minutes.
